1
00:01:11,079 --> 00:01:12,920
Suspect's Toyota SUV entering from north gate.

2
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:14,200
All units, stand by.

3
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,120
Prepare to move in.

4
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:17,200
Copy that.

5
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:22,239
Hey, sorry about that.

6
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:24,400
Gate's broken. Go around the back.

7
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:27,079
Cut the crap.

8
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,079
Open this gate, now.

9
00:01:28,079 --> 00:01:29,519
It really won't open. It's broken.

10
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,359
Alright, got it.

11
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:36,680
Reporting, Captain Li.

12
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,560
Red Glove confirmed.

13
00:01:41,239 --> 00:01:41,799
Move in.

14
00:02:03,159 --> 00:02:03,760
Get out of the car!

15
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,480
Get out!

16
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:07,079
Out! Out!

17
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:07,719
Hands behind your head!

18
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,560
Out! Out! Out!

19
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:08,960
Get out of the car!

20
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,520
Move!

21
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:10,960
What's going on?

22
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,840
What did I even do?

23
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,759
On what grounds are you arresting me?

24
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:16,960
Cut the crap.

25
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,400
Get up.

26
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,840
Why are you driving Ma Shijiang's car?

27
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,719
Why are you wearing red gloves?

28
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,840
I was drinking with Brother Ma at Wild Rose.

29
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,680
He said he'd be partying all night.

30
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,479
He asked me to go feed his dog.

31
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,120
Take him away.

32
00:02:45,919 --> 00:02:46,560
Boss.

33
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,800
There was a taxi at that intersection.

34
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,800
Something's off. It sat there for 30 seconds.

35
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:51,599
Hold on.

36
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:53,879
The other entrance is at the south gate.

37
00:02:53,879 --> 00:02:54,960
Why was it heading to the north gate?

38
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,199
I'd just pulled up to the complex,

39
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:59,000
when Brother Ma called to hurry me back.

40
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:04,280
That taxi stopped on a green light,

41
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,120
but turned left on a red.

42
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,120
Your suspicion makes sense.

43
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:14,159
Ma Shijiang was likely in that car.

44
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:17,919
Did you get the plate number?

45
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:21,599
It looked like an 8 or a 6.

46
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:22,560
Wang.

47
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,240
Take a team to Wild Rose immediately.

48
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:24,960
Liu.

49
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,240
Notify all patrol units.

50
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,960
Do an urgent sweep across the west district,

51
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,599
for all taxis with plates ending in 6 or 8.

52
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,639
You, come with me.

53
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:31,960
Move.

54
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,159
Where's Ma Shijiang?

55
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,879
He left before midnight.

56
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:10,919
What number is that?

57
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,080
It's a six.

58
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:16,759
Taxi ahead, pull over to the side!

59
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:20,079
Attention all units.

60
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,879
Suspicious taxi spotted on Xiguan Street.

61
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:23,600
Heading west on Wuzhuang Street.

62
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:25,000
Go after him!

63
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:47,839
Hey, sweetheart.

64
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,240
Come dance with me.

65
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,600
Sir, I don't know how to dance.

66
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,439
What are you afraid of?

67
00:04:58,959 --> 00:04:59,959
I won't bite.

68
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,839
It's fine if you can't dance.

69
00:05:06,199 --> 00:05:07,040
Just have a drink with me.

70
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,399
Sir, I just sell drinks.

71
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:11,199
I don't drink with customers.

72
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,319
Don't act all innocent.

73
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:20,720
You're lucky to meet Brother Ma.

74
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,439
Brother Ma has just two strong points:

75
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:23,800
He's rich,

76
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,519
and he treats women well.

77
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,800
Finish this bottle with me,

78
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,399
and all this is yours.

79
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:38,600
Once you're done,

80
00:05:39,319 --> 00:05:40,040
come with me.

81
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:43,040
I'll give you another five thousand.

82
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:46,360
Sir, I really can't drink.

83
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,680
Enough, Xiao Yun.

84
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:50,000
Stop pretending.

85
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,839
Brother Ma doesn't go for just any girl.

86
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:03,279
You think you're too good for him?

87
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:06,720
One word from him and you're out of here.

88
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:07,839
You got that?

89
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,560
Don't ruin another one of my girls.

90
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,399
Let me feed it to you.

91
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,519
Loosen up!

92
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,560
Who is it?

93
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:54,959
Lay low for a while.

94
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,720
The cops are onto you now.

95
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,480
What?

96
00:06:59,439 --> 00:07:00,439
Are you sure about that?

97
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,920
Don't mess with me.

98
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,399
Hello? Hello?

99
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,839
Using a voice changer for a phone call?

100
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,959
Who's he trying to scare?

101
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,920
Hey girl, where are you headed?

102
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,319
Let me give you a ride.

103
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,560
Driver.

104
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:26,600
Where are you taking me?

105
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:28,399
I'm not feeling well.

106
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:29,279
I feel like I'm gonna throw up.

107
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,360
Driver!

108
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,720
Stop the car! Stop!

109
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,399
Stop the car!

110
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:52,120
Stop! Stop the car!

111
00:09:01,279 --> 00:09:02,919
Help! Help me!

112
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:01,240
Boss.

113
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:20,320
Boss.

114
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:22,120
Are you alright?

115
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,639
Captain Zhao, we've got this.

116
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:37,399
Why don't you go rest in the office?

117
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:40,000
I'm fine.

118
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,440
That animal.

119
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:45,159
He filmed himself assaulting those women.

120
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:47,720
Captain Zhao, Captain Li.

121
00:10:48,759 --> 00:10:50,639
We searched Ma Shijiang's home thoroughly.

122
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:52,159
We brought back all the useful evidence.

123
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:53,320
Any computers?

124
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,039
One desktop.

125
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:55,879
And one laptop.

126
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,720
Get them to tech for decryption right away.

127
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,159
Ma Shijiang likely uploaded

128
00:10:59,159 --> 00:11:00,639
the assault videos online.

129
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,519
Yes, sir.

130
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:10,840
After tech cracked Ma Shijiang's computer,

131
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:14,039
we found lots of porn and violent videos.

132
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,799
Based on the footage,

133
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,799
the district station's two rape cases,

134
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:21,440
realtor Meng Xiaoyi's rape and carving,

135
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:24,960
and the rape-murder of Liu Xiang,

136
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,720
all were committed by Ma Shijiang.

137
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:28,440
Was there...

138
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,879
Was there a video of Ruolan being assaulted?

139
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,600
Answer me. Was there?

140
00:11:38,039 --> 00:11:38,639
No.

141
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:41,720
There wasn't.

142
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,080
Captain Zhao.

143
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:44,639
There really wasn't.

144
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,919
You're all in on this, lying to me, aren't you?

145
00:11:55,039 --> 00:11:55,679
Boss.

146
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,720
In Ma Shijiang's camera and computer,

147
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,799
we found no footage of Ruolan's assault.

148
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,399
Why are the others all there,

149
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,000
but Ruolan's is the only one missing?

150
00:12:07,279 --> 00:12:07,919
Captain Zhao.

151
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,320
We're really not hiding anything.

152
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:10,679
There really isn't any.

153
00:12:20,159 --> 00:12:21,000
Back to the case.

154
00:12:26,639 --> 00:12:28,440
Tech unit cracked Ma Shijiang's computer.

155
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:30,600
Based on his network settings

156
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,639
and browsing history, analysis shows

157
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:34,519
he was uploading illegal videos

158
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:36,360
online for profit.

159
00:12:37,679 --> 00:12:38,840
Is Ma Shijiang the mastermind?

160
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,440
From what we know so far,

161
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:43,480
he's just a key link in the criminal chain.

162
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:44,519
His handler

163
00:12:44,519 --> 00:12:45,919
must be a tech expert

164
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,320
with strong counter-surveillance skills.

165
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:51,159
How long until Tech makes a breakthrough?

166
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,679
The investigation is extremely difficult.

167
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,320
All data is multi-layer encrypted,

168
00:12:57,879 --> 00:12:59,600
hard to trace by standard monitoring.

169
00:12:59,759 --> 00:13:01,360
Which further severs the link between

170
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,480
real identities and online activity.

171
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,840
Jiang Han, Lin Xue.

172
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:11,840
Stay in close contact with Tech unit.

173
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:13,080
Share all information.

174
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,600
Even if we have to dig up the city,

175
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,279
we must drag out the mastermind

176
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:18,200
behind these livestreams

177
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,559
and shut them down for good.

178
00:13:19,799 --> 00:13:20,519
Yes, sir.

179
00:13:26,559 --> 00:13:27,120
Bro.

180
00:13:27,879 --> 00:13:29,279
What's so important it has to be said here?

181
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:34,440
Chief Xing sent you out of town for Ma.

182
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,120
You already know.

183
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,320
He slipped right through our hands last time.

184
00:13:43,039 --> 00:13:44,240
We have to catch him this time.

185
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:47,039
Have you ever wondered,

186
00:13:48,159 --> 00:13:49,639
with such a tight lockdown,

187
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,600
how he managed to escape?

188
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,240
I just can't figure it out.

189
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:57,240
Why did the operation that night fail?

190
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,759
We immediately deployed

191
00:13:59,039 --> 00:14:00,679
an extremely thorough plan.

192
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:01,799
Airport,

193
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:03,519
train station,

194
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:04,879
bus station,

195
00:14:06,639 --> 00:14:08,639
every route out of the city,

196
00:14:08,879 --> 00:14:09,840
we had them all covered.

197
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:12,600
He couldn't leave Fengdu without a trace.

198
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,519
The key to all this lies in

199
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:21,080
where Ma Shijiang vanished.

200
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:23,639
Wuzhuang Town, Yong'an District.

201
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,519
We turned Wuzhuang upside down those days.

202
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,639
Found no trace of Ma Shijiang.

203
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,799
We must've missed something.

204
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,759
Did you find something?

205
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,960
I don't have solid proof yet.

206
00:14:50,679 --> 00:14:51,960
Once we catch Ma Shijiang,

207
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,759
everything will become clear.

208
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:57,679
Boss.

209
00:14:58,399 --> 00:14:59,200
It's time.

210
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,320
I have to head out.

211
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:01,840
Kaiyang.

212
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,320
Leave this chance to me.

213
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:13,120
If I don't catch that bastard myself,

214
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,159
I'll never be able to face Ruolan again.

215
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:17,039
Of course I understand.

216
00:15:18,679 --> 00:15:19,360
But by protocol...

217
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,840
I'll take all the consequences.
